autoscope.driver

Class Autoscope

  • java.lang.Object
    • autoscope.driver.Autoscope

  • public final class Autoscope
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains methods called to perform automation tasks on Android and iOS. (tap, scroll, type, swipe, etc.)
